reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Made my Rubbermaid lobby dustpans functional again
reviews.reviewText: I have several Rubbermaid lobby dustpans in my facility that all failed - the edge bows up a bit in the center, leading to any dust and smaller particles going under the dustpan instead of into it. These flexible strips are the perfect answer to make dustpan meet ground, as intended, so sweeping does what it should.Don't know if it was needed but I added a bit of clear rubber adhesive to the ends of the strip, to help ensure it stays in place.
